Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chance to be a hero is long gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dug myself into a hole with no way out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back against the wall... I \Nmean, how could I resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This wasn't supposed to \Nhappen," I keep denying
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could just disappear... \NI can't stand myself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moping around, spouting lies, \Ngrieving a broken heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hold on desperately to these \Nfeelings and shut my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why does this stupid \Nguilt refuse to go away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.63,0:00:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suffocate under its weight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chance to be a hero is long gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always discouraged by my weaknesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drop to my knees and grovel at your feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,clinging selfishly to \Nthe hope for forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dug myself into a hole with no way out...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full of regret and powerless to change,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel my heart being torn apart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.58,0:01:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on this night of endless shame and despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.38,0:01:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I get my act together?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.63,0:01:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got nothing but this pathetic self of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that voice...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lay low in here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the MEANING of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this how you treat people\Nafter gettin' your pickle licked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your mouth shut, I'm BEGGING you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:02:01.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 2: Peter Grill and \Nthe Future Father-in-Law
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Luvellia-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Wh-what's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sweating up a storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TRAINING!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, I was in the middle \Nof my training routine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd expect nothing less.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maintaining a strict regimen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rather than allowing\Nyour accomplishments to inflate your ego...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly why you are suited\Nto become my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a reason I've come to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we return to Guild Headquarters today...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I plan on informing my \Nfather of our engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll lend me your support, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're the only \Nwoman I've got eyes for!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I entered the tournament for a chance\Nto earn her hand in marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting the green light from the Guildmaster\Nwould be a perfect ending to our story...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Father...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were so enthusiastic \Nabout the idea of the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Fighting Tournament Champion\Nbecoming your son-in-law!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter Grill...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attempting to deceive my daughter, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YOUR DEATH SHALL BE SWIFT!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cannot accept the \Nreality of our relationship,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am prepared to cut ties with you\Nand move away from home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A life without my precious Luvellia...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come to this \Ndecision of my own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's done for...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given the circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it appears I've been left with no choice\Nbut to grant you my blessing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mark my words, Peter Grill...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will RUE this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You impudent, conniving...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it be known:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Guild hereby recognizes the engagement\Nbetween Peter Grill and Lady Luvellia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make preparations for a feast in their honor,\Nand to celebrate our triumph in the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I'm surprised you managed\Nto convince the Guildmaster...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I was quite nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've seen for yourself how \Nruthless my father can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it was my faith in you that gave\Nme the strength to confront him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that she trusts me so deeply...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guilt is eating me alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If word got out about my \Nfling with the Ogre sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Guildmaster would wring my neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if Luvellia-senpai somehow found out...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda late, but we wanna sincerely congratulate\Nyou on goin' public with your engagement!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured, we shall cheer \Nyou on from the sidelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must've had a change of heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that note, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hopin' to get a big ol' batch\Nof baby batter again tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'mind if we bump uglies right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.19,0:05:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHO IN THE WORLD WOULDN'T MIND?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look... You heard the news, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm officially engaged \Nto Luvellia-senpai now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This poses no risk to our objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We merely wish to conceive a child\Nwith the world's strongest warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A relationship born of convenience and\Ndevoid of affection is more than adequate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're insane...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oopsie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make a deal, Peter Grill...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We promise never to disclose\Nthis little arrangement of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In return, you shall continue to\Nsupply us with your sweet seed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until we've sucessfully become \Npregnant... at the least!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those footsteps...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time to put on pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's my next move...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little farther...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sure was quick...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was having another \None of his outbursts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:07:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Guildmaster gets angry,\Nyou're just about the only one who can calm him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter Grill...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to speak with Luvellia.\NLend me your seat, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was totally unprepared for\Nsomething like this to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving up my seat is the obvious answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HOWEVER...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'd catch sight of the \Nnaked Ogre sisters...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone would realize that my junk's been\Nflappin' in the wind this whole time...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father! I shall accompany \Nyou somewhere private...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense! Stay right where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you didn't hear me, Peter-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what now...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's gotta be some \Nway out of this, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run that by me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just refuse an order?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of giving up\Nmy place at Senpai's side...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider this proof of my commitment to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Peter-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Insolent brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to sway my darling Luvellia\Nwith your empty words again, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-am I busted?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess what, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I get bigger, I'm gonna be your wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cannot accept our relationship,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am prepared to cut ties with you\Nand move away from home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How loathsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I require more alcohol to \Nendure this wretched party...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-did he take the bait...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:09:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had anyone stand up to\Nmy father like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This merely reinforces my belief that you're the\Nonly man fit to become my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Peter-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one for \Nme, Luvellia-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father's lost his temper again...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, Peter-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peekaboo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like that pesky \Ndistraction is finally gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-hey! Quit stickin' your \Nhead out of my crotch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let us continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard what I said back there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai is the one \Nand only woman I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crazy if you think I'll make\Nanother mistake with the two of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:09:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might claim to have an iron will,\Nbut your downstairs brain suggests otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A physiological response like \Nthis has nothing to do with
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long 'til you start \Nsingin' a different tune?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to find out... Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai has faith \Nin me, of all people...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made the same damn mistake...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are people only capable of rational\Nthought AFTER they've already screwed up...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It started out as a simple crush
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, you were my \Nbiggest source of strength
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Till death do us part, \Nlet's grow old together
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my sincerest wish:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me, stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long time, by my side for all eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beaten down by our daily struggles
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or soaked by a storm of rage;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get drenched, I won't hesitate
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be the umbrella that shields you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so cold... I'm by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good enough for me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my rock, my strength
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That smile of yours puts my soul at ease
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could search the whole world over
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And find no one like you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my rock, my strength
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the sight of you fills my heart with joy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much it may hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pledge my life to protecting you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found you... Peter Grill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Sir Peter Grill,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats on going public \Nwith your engagement!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-san, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:11.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 3: Peter Grill and \NRelationships with Elves
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be happy as a \Nclam right about now, eh?